<h1 style="text-align: center;">About us</h1>

<p style="text-align: center;"><br />We understand that choosing the right early childhood development centre is a complex and difficult decision for parents we therefore aim to provide parents with a platform that ensures that their children are placed in registered early childhood development centres that adhere to the standards set by the government. To ensure that children are afforded a healthy, clean and safe learning environment. We also aim to create a safe and secure line of communication between early childhood centres parents and staff, it is a replacement to the information daily sheet and much more.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1 style="text-align: center;">Philosophy</h1>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br />We believe that parents play a vital role in their child&rsquo;s development, and so do early childhood development centres, thus we aim to provide a platform that enables a safe and secure line of communication between early childhood development centres, staff and parents. We also aim to ensure that children are cared for, guided towards attaining their optimal level of intellectual, cultural, and physical potential in a warm, friendly, disciplined and stimulating environment.</p>
